    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "紧追莱姬希途中，马斯古拉向众人\\n讲述了过去的故事。制造出“战斗人偶”的\\n麦斯特罗赋予了莱姬希最高指挥权，\\n赋予了马斯古拉彻底摧毁莱姬希的力量，\\n更给予了二人以“心”。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "莱姬希在前方约1920步远的位置。\\n我们抓紧时间吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好厉害……\\n竟能将位置能掌握得如此精确。\\n战斗人偶都是这样吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我和莱姬希比较特殊……\\n我们是被特别制造的人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "特别制造吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉……你们是为了战斗\\n而被造出来的兵器吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "卢卡！不要一上来\\n就问这种问题……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "没关系，因为事实确实如此。\\n我们是用于战斗的兵器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "但是，至少马斯古拉看上去不像。\\n这就是你所说的“特殊”吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我可以讲一些过去的事吗……\\n距今300年前的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我们战斗人偶是狄涅尔帝国\\n在300年前制造出来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "但是，制造我们的人——\\n麦斯特罗说过，\\n其实他并不想制造我们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "并不想制造你们？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是的。麦斯特罗……\\n他是狄涅尔人，\\n因为某些原因才听命于帝国。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "所以麦斯特罗曾经说过，\\n他并不想制造用于战争的兵器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "制造者……也就是像\\n亲生父母一样的存在吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "要是被父母说什么\\n根本不想制造的话，\\n感觉你们好可怜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "可怜？不，我们并不可怜。\\n我很庆幸被麦斯特罗制造出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "麦斯特罗并没有\\n把我们当成兵器对待。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "甚至因为不想让我们上战场\\n而多次违抗帝国的命令。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是这样啊……\\n的确，和听到的传闻相比，\\n亲眼见到战斗人偶的人很少。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "对抗帝国的人们之中\\n甚至有人认为战斗人偶\\n只是捏造出来的谣言。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "这都是多亏麦斯特罗。\\n可惜……麦斯特罗是人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是生命有限的人类……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "他去世了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是的。早在狄涅尔帝国\\n和阿尔贝琉斯的军队交战前，\\n他就已经病倒了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "但是他为了防止自己死后\\n有人操纵我们去战斗\\n而留下了一些措施。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "措施？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是的。其中一个是\\n指挥官莱姬希的命令\\n优先于其他任何人的命令。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "而且，如果莱姬希彻底停下来，\\n所有战斗人偶也会跟着停下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "而另一个措施则是，\\n麦斯特罗制造了一个足以\\n彻底摧毁莱姬希的战斗人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "居然有战斗人偶能彻底摧毁\\n那个失控的莱姬希？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "那就是我——马斯古拉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你能……\\n彻底摧毁莱姬希！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是的，我就是为此\\n而被制造出来的战斗人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "可、可是，\\n你讨厌战斗吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "为什么会让你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "恐怕……\\n这正是麦斯特罗的目的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "他留下的最后一项措施，\\n就是给予了我和莱姬希“心”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "心？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "他赋予了我们自行判断正误……\\n判断善恶的功能。\\n我把这种功能称为“心”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "而现在，莱姬希的“心”\\n已经坏掉了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "所以才会变成那样，\\n无论对谁都发起攻击。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我之所以特别讨厌争斗，\\n也是因为有这个功能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我如果破坏了莱姬希，\\n所有战斗人偶就都会停止。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "所以，为了不让我草率地做决定，\\n麦斯特罗才给了我\\n讨厌争斗的“心”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真的是这样吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "麦斯特罗是个\\n心地善良的人对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那么，也许麦斯特罗\\n只是希望自己的孩子\\n也能拥有一颗善良的心呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "孩、孩子……我是……\\n麦斯特罗的孩子？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊，听你那说法，\\n肯定会这么认为啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "所以，麦斯特罗\\n之所以给你善良的“心”，\\n一定跟功能或作用无关。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，也许他只是希望你\\n能成为一个善良的人罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "尤蒂尔、卢卡……\\n你们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "你们很善良……\\n简直就像麦斯特罗一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "所幸，300年前麦斯特罗死后不久，\\n魔神就被封印了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我们也无需依靠\\n麦斯特罗留下的措施\\n而陷入了沉睡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我一直以为……\\n也许不会再醒来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "然而我认为时隔300年醒来、\\n与你们的相遇并不是偶然。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "也许，为了你们而使用\\n麦斯特罗遗留之物的时刻\\n已经到了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}